ActSpecial Economic Measures Act
SubjectSpecial Economic Measures Permit Authorization Order
PrecisSPECIAL ECONOMIC MEASURES PERMIT AUTHORIZATION ORDER in order to authorize the Minister of Foreign Affairs to issue both individual permits and general permits that would allow persons in Canada or any Canadian outside Canada to carry out a specified activity or transaction, or any class of activity or transaction that is restricted or prohibited under certain regulations.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2025-0050 Publication Date: 2025-03-12
